2009-05-21
			  Kai Cacti Templates

Cacti template files are used for drawing status of Kai node obtained
by the stats command.

1. Pre-requisite

- PECL memcached library, which can be downloaded the following URL:

  http://pecl.php.net/package/memcached

2. Installation

- install kai.php into the Cacti scripts directory, as follows:

  $ cp -p kai.php <cacti-path>/scripts/

- After logging-in Cacti, then choose "Import Templates" from the
  left-side menu bar, and import the following XML files:

  cacti_graph_template_kai_transfer.xml
  cacti_graph_template_kai_curr_items.xml
  cacti_graph_template_kai_command.xml
  cacti_graph_template_kai_byte.xml
  cacti_data_template_kai.xml
